events.text: Finally back home, uff. Let’s see what I need to do.
I try to vacuum every week. Sometimes I don’t manage because of work. Remember that one time when my manager called me at 22:00?! I was just about to go to bed. I always go to bed at 22:00.
Public transport used to be reimbursed by the company. I wish they didn’t cancel that.
Ψ400 for health insurance but I am never sick! I would lose my job if I were. Being 5 minutes late is already a huge problem.
The certainty of having the same dinner every day, ahhhhh...
Hmmm, what did I just agree to? It said something about that the death is only the beginning??, hmmm, that’s weird, I probably misread… I am sure it was just a dumb marketing headline…
Let’s delete spam first.
Hope he can take me on Saturday. I can’t miss work.
I wonder why we have to make to-do lists every day. Who is it for? I doubt my manager reads all the to-do lists. Just our office is around 300 people.
Spick-and-span. I should refill my fridge. I wish I could go to the market but it’s always closed before I get home from work.
Hmm, am I forgetting something before I go to bed?
Finally, this was a long day and tomorrow will be the same. Sometimes I wish for a change.
I can’t pay my bills? This always works. I don’t want to get a fine.
Maybe I could try asking my neighbor if he got my mail by accident.
Hello Tom, did you receive my mail by accident perhaps?
Good afternoon, do we know each other? I don’t have time for this. Please, leave me alone.
I should get some money before my bank card stops working.
Just a simple quick dinner. This was a stressful day. I don’t have the energy for anything else.
Hmm, am I forgetting something before I finish this stressful day?
This was a very distressing and worrisome day. Let’s hope it was just a bug in the system.
